title: FSU Remains Unbeaten in Four-Set Win Over Wolfpack (Florida State Seminoles)
text: ( Source : Florida State Seminoles ) RALEIGH, N.C. - Sparked by Nicole Walch 's match-high 23 kills the 18 th -ranked Florida State volleyball program completed its sweep of the state of North Carolina with a 25-18, 33-31, 22-25, 25-20 victory
